ogy 51, 499–507&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="e28o1LB7"&gt;&lt;i&gt;[11]  Tapanila, L. and Roberts, E.M. (2012) The earliest evidence of  holometabolan insect pupation in conifer wood. PLoS One 7, e31668&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="uYBvhRiO"&gt;&lt;i&gt;[12]  Li Ya, Li Yan-Da, Wang Yong-Dong*, Schneider Harald, Shi Gong-Le, 2022.  Re-appraisal of lacewing mimicry of liverworts from the mid-Cretaceous  Kachin amber, Myanmar with a description of Selaginella cretacea sp.  nov. (Selaginellales, Selaginellaceae). Cretaceous  Research,133:105143.&lt;a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.1016/j.cretres.2022.105143" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;doi.org/10.1016/j.cretr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;es.2022.105143&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="0PNofnPj"&gt;作者：王冠群、王博、潘浩晨&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="tuTJl19i"&gt;作者单位：中国科学院南京地质古生物研究所&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kbB6NMGOEf_9ziAGtLTfSw" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-300f6ddc37714bf05995aa28ae634d27_qhd.jpg" data-image-width="755" data-image-height="321" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;用《孙子兵法》的方式打开昆虫帝国 | 中生代往事（中）&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p data-pid="EyzWAV41"&gt;&lt;a class="member_mention" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/da971e1f564d733611f6a9a51930c4aa" data-hash="da971e1f564d733611f6a9a51930c4aa" data-hovercard="p$b$da971e1f564d733611f6a9a51930c4aa"&gt;@中国科普博览&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="member_mention" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/df247603a41cf58a466551f0ab09d525" data-hash="df247603a41cf58a466551f0ab09d525" data-hovercard="p$b$df247603a41cf58a466551f0ab09d525"&gt;@科普中国&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="member_mention" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/0f2006385065c411ad6d08b4fc62b788" data-hash="0f2006385065c411ad6d08b4fc62b788" data-hovercard="p$b$0f2006385065c411ad6d08b4fc62b788"&gt;@知乎科学&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
